New work for @grist about the indigenous history of the American Chestnut tree. A fungal blight brought on by European colonization wiped out the species. Now a transgenic tree is being grown, which raises the question: “What good is bringing back a species, without also restoring its traditional relationships with the indigenous peoples who helped it flourish?” A really interesting one thanks to AD: Mia Torres 
.
.
.
.
#americanchestnut #biotechnology #editorialillustration #editorialillustrator #illustrationartists #torontoart #gouachepainting #itsnicethat
